foreBridgeExtensions.description: Fore ASX ethernet bridge mib extensions.

bridgeDataSource.name: bridgeDataSource
bridgeDataSource.description: This object specifies the name of the bridge that is currently visable via SNMP accesses to the Bridge MIB (RFC-1493). If there is no bridge of that name, then accesses to objects in the Bridge MIB will return noSuchName errors. The factory default value for this object is 'default'

bridgeNumberOfEntities.name: bridgeNumberOfEntities
bridgeNumberOfEntities.description: This object specifies the number of logical bridges in the system.

bridgeStpAtmPortTable.name: bridgeStpAtmPortTable
bridgeStpAtmPortTable.description: A table that contains atm port-specific information for the Spanning Tree Protocol.

bridgeStpAtmPortEntry.name: bridgeStpAtmPortEntry
bridgeStpAtmPortEntry.description: A list of information maintained by every atm port about the Spanning Tree Protocol state for that port.

bridgeStpAtmPort.name: bridgeStpAtmPort
bridgeStpAtmPort.description: The port number of the port for which this entry contains Spanning Tree Protocol management information.

bridgeStpAtmPortPriority.name: bridgeStpAtmPortPriority
bridgeStpAtmPortPriority.description: The value of the priority field which is contained in the first (in network byte order) octet of the (2 octet long) Port ID. The other octet of the Port ID is given by the value of bridgeStpAtmPort.

bridgeStpAtmPortState.name: bridgeStpAtmPortState
bridgeStpAtmPortState.description: The port's current state as defined by application of the Spanning Tree Protocol. This state controls what action a port takes on reception of a frame.

bridgeStpAtmPortEnable.name: bridgeStpAtmPortEnable
bridgeStpAtmPortEnable.description: The enabled/disabled status of the port.

bridgeStpAtmPortPathCost.name: bridgeStpAtmPortPathCost
bridgeStpAtmPortPathCost.description: The contribution of this port to the path cost of paths towards the spanning tree root which include this port.

bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedRoot.name: bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedRoot
bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedRoot.description: The unique Bridge Identifier of the Bridge recorded as the Root in the Configuration BPDUs transmitted by the Designated Bridge for the segment to which the port is attached.

bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedCost.name: bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedCost
bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedCost.description: The path cost of the Designated Port of the segment connected to this port. This value is compared to the Root Path Cost field in received bridge PDUs.

bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedBridge.name: bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedBridge
bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedBridge.description: The Bridge Identifier of the bridge which this port considers to be the Designated Bridge for this port's segment.

bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedPort.name: bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedPort
bridgeStpAtmPortDesignatedPort.description: The Port Identifier of the port on the Designated Bridge for this port's segment.

bridgeStpAtmPortForwardTransitions.name: bridgeStpAtmPortForwardTransitions
bridgeStpAtmPortForwardTransitions.description: The number of times this port has transitioned from the Learning state to the Forwarding state.

bridgeStpEnable.name: bridgeStpEnable
bridgeStpEnable.description: The enabled/disabled status of the bridge.
